# API Design Standards

## Structure
/api/v1/resource

## Response Format
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "",
  "data": {},
  "errors": null
}

## Rules
- Always use API Resources
- Never return raw models
- Always version APIs

## Status Codes
- 200 OK
- 201 Created
- 400 Bad Request
- 401 Unauthorized
- 403 Forbidden
- 422 Validation Error
- 500 Server Error